 23â†’// Storage is an implementation of git.Storer that stores data on memory, being
 24â†’// ephemeral. The use of this storage should be done in controlled environments,
 25â†’// since the representation in memory of some repository can fill the machine
 26â†’// memory. in the other hand this storage has the best performance.
 27â†’type Storage struct {
 28â†’	ConfigStorage
 29â†’	ObjectStorage
 30â†’	ShallowStorage
 31â†’	IndexStorage
 32â†’	ReferenceStorage
 33â†’	ModuleStorage
